value: Breeds on islands off southeastern Australia, in Bass Strait, off southern Tasmania, and mainly off coasts of New Zealand from extreme north to Foveaux Strait (also Cape Kidnappers on mainland). Ranges northwest to Pt. Cloates, Western Australia, north to Mackay, Queensland, east to Chatham Islands, south to Auckland Islands and Campbell Island.
